how do you stay in shape on a busy schedule i'm but i want to stay in shape women in my family generally gain weight pretty darn fast in their teens unfortunately i'm only and but i don't want to gain any more plus my mom nags me that i'm going to get fat i can find time to do curl ups and push ups but during school i don't have the time to go running every day how do you stay in shape on a busy schedule try to have as little down time as possible stay active as mush as possible avoid snacking when you can and just always have something to do at all times during school there is not a whole lot you can do except when you are walking to class try speed walking burn the calories when you can but do not starve yourself you will just get sick Dieting Anorexia nervosa Bodybuilding Aerial (dance move) Binge eating disorder Carburetor Weight training Obesity Social rule Equine conformation Fat Man and Little Boy (Simpsons) The Adventures of Pete & Pete Iditarod Joke Sailing Super Size Me Atkins Nutritional Approach Explosive material Low-carbohydrate diet Paragliding Fasting Internal ballistics Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban Bacon The Rock and Roll Hall of Fame's 500 Songs that Shaped Rock and Roll Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Driver's license Fast food Body type (exercise) Unreal Cranford, New Jersey Calorie restriction Curling Phoebe Buffay's songs Slim Fast Kurt Cobain Swimming Acorn Power-up Monday Night Football Sonic the Hedgehog Futurama (TV series - season 2) Protein Hiking Exercise Kodocha Milk United Parcel Service Marching band Little Britain Lindy Basic The Supremes The Ashlee Simpson Show Computer virus Decompression sickness Breastfeeding Teacher's Pet (Disney) Time Out of Mind United Kingdom corporation tax Shen Gong Wu Billboard Hot 100 Computer bus Bubble Bobble Calorie Garfield Treehouse of Horror V Thread (computer science) Requirements analysis Soap opera Back to the Future CPU cache Flash (comics) Handloading Bulk vending Weig